== Access ==

The site is a 10-minute walk west from {{ill|Furuichi Station|ja|古市駅|12=draft|12=draft}} on the {{ill|Kintetsu Minami Osaka Line|ja|近鉄南大阪線|12=draft|12=draft}}, passing the {{ill|Shiratori Intersection|ja|白鳥交差点|12=draft|12=draft}} on National Route 166.

