== Access ==

The site is a 10-minute walk west from [[:en:Furuichi Station|Furuichi Station]] on the [[:en:Minami Osaka Line|Kintetsu Minami Osaka Line]], passing the {{ill|Shiratori Intersection|ja|白鳥交差点|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiratori Intersection|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} on National Route 166.

